Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:07.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Can't you see that you are sweet？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:16.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh Let me love you so
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げる空は遠いけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.50,0:00:37.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱えきれない夢がある
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.10,0:00:44.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}創られた世界の中を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.50,0:00:52.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抜け出して　自由になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.50,0:00:59.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走り続けて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.50,0:01:05.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に屆けば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.50,0:01:11.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風になれると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:17.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう信じてるから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.50,0:01:23.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never give up forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.29,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹的盡頭有什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裏面裝了什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.31,0:02:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是38街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.04,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是黃綠色的大型貨櫃拖車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自藍梅大道向貝拉地區駛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那種工廠用的好大好大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共4輛 希望你能查查其去向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.89,0:03:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察用電腦不是很容易查得到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽沒聽我說啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了！聽到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車牌號碼我也記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.20,0:03:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S63D0018 聽人家說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 玩偵探遊戲也得適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這可是肇事逃逸事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒被撞了 你看看這兒也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是16號車 即刻往貝拉地區24號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.62,0:03:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查交通事故的肇事嫌疑人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.53,0:03:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還記得駕駛員的長相吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 記得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S63D0018 號碼符合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這輛車沒錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.78,0:04:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向左些 再來 再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.79,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方人員 有事相問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.99,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 打開倉門 請稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兒的負責人是哪位？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.41,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這裏的經理 有何貴幹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.82,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面那輛拖車是貴公司的車嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.72,0:04:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是本公司借用的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來問問看如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.27,0:05:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 過來 這裏有沒有撞你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等等 一定是搞錯了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?還記得嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叔叔 他撞了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.19,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上六點你在何處？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從港口開往這兒的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路線呢 經過了哪兒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.36,0:05:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自藍梅大道去向38街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 和那小孩的說詞一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑 那小鬼一定是在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.50,0:05:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很可疑 好像隱瞞了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不查查貨櫃的裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來查查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經理 開關在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊開一下好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.82,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來 得刷卡才能開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡片…卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你忘我了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾？你是亞爾 都長這麼大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生 對不起 被車子撞的事都是胡說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因父母離婚而與哥哥離散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然在路上見到哥哥開拖車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4年未見了 想見他 才說謊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傷是跌傷的 和車無關 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 怎麼可以對警察說謊呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是的 竟帶警官來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要玩真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家不知道地方的關係嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道又想如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入？這可不是戰爭遊戲啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉 這小鬼要如何處置？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫亞爾·佛烈德是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔是隊長吧?讓我也加入嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當個吉翁軍的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想當兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入可以 但有個條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,條件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.58,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 不能將我們的事對任何人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應 不會對任何人說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.19,0:07:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點 想問些有關你拍的錄影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.89,0:07:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兒是8號門 貨櫃就在這地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概已運至12區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何你會這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自8號門進的貨大多以C起重機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送往12區之故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 你真是個乖巧的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那貨櫃裏面有什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查這個便是我們的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天這就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的幫忙 這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.17,0:08:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們部隊的徽章 不要弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有人問起就說是撿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 隊長閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.88,0:08:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼要送你回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這車子真這麼希奇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員開的呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡會拍馬屁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼暫時由巴尼監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.03,0:09:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉不就沒事了或關在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼不知哪天會壞了大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想惹出風波嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 也有巴尼做的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在太空中被擊中真慘透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 是在無重力狀態下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在駕駛艙中血四處飛飄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像極了地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.77,0:09:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也眼睜睜失去了無數戰友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實像你這樣的小鬼 是不會有這樣的經歷的不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼也有殺過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也不是想殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不先下手 會反遭其害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好擊毀目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴酷的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 要是我打下那一部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能成為王牌駕駛員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方很厲害嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我太大意了 那天是休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻又突然有了任務 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.91,0:10:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兒右轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 雖說是放假 也得說一聲才出門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.93,0:10:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校來了封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師為了成績的事想找媽媽談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前的考試成績很差是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.94,0:10:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何隱瞞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.14,0:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 要玩的話也得先將書念好啊！知道了沒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.60,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽去參加個婦女團體的聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好做作業哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X減Y等於…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！媽媽！快報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有小偷 逮到小偷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 這傢夥想潛入你家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.35,0:12:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.69,0:12:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 別報警了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好 還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.63,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在很抱歉 誤會你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.54,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不知道亞爾有個哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.08,0:13:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是同父異母的 父親年輕時生了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.09,0:13:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似遭親人反對 而後便分手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美津子知道你們的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密 所以才偷偷來會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪會被誤以為是小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原諒她吧!被她占了便宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.01,0:13:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很對不起 我忍不住…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還真是個好強的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟跟人家去加入聯邦軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯原來是個軍人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是情報搜集的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是拿著槍和別人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼可是個真正的軍人也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:14:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 已退伍了 現是後備軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是才回到這個衛星殖民地的是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作也在這兒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工廠找了份與機械相關的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待 打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必急嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有約…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭不礙事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.79,0:14:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度的傷不礙事的 這個謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.80,0:14:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯 晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光從外表看 還不曉得她的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為她人還不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.42,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑!出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.37,0:15:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾…你一整天都跑哪兒去啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱們去公園打仗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧！今天我很忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝上鎖釘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.90,0:15:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從哪兒開始？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.91,0:15:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來裏面裝的是機動戰士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 快鎖上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個和聯邦軍作戰是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個用以逃出衛星殖民地時用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是打 只是用以逃避而已？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.07,0:16:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若聯邦軍追擊過來又另當別論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 駕駛員就讓巴尼當好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他再打下一架就是王牌了駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.98,0:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 駕駛員已內定為米舍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.68,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何巴尼不行呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為米舍較為老練之故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.49,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 很不好意思 只差一架就能成為王牌了駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.69,0:16:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有4架啊 我還以為有二十架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.76,0:17:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯 到次暫告一段落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5分鐘後有一新的程式 再挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.06,0:17:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反應速度資料呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平均值30%的增幅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距80%還有段距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“艾里克斯”乘坐的感覺如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全景熒幕和磁場的感覺如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快得叫人好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼敏感的機器實戰中用得了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全賴駕駛員的技術了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.69,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我駕駛不了“艾里克斯”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣 這是新人類專用機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認可你的技術 但仍須些時日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能駕駛得了它 得有過人的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要像“白色基地”上的駕駛員那樣的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 咱們回去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.39,0:18:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的秘密基地是找不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是隊長難得託付於我的任務吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 聯邦為何要隱瞞基地之事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.44,0:19:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Side6與聯邦的安全保障條約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還未正式締結之故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.35,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是目前對聯邦的行動仍有制約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.16,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦車牌的車子怎出奇地少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若咱們找出了聯邦的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長會不會改變想法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變什麼想法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員的人選啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會是你而不是米舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不在意這事兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為王牌的機會還多的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 回去吧 回去吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？亞爾 喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.40,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了 巴尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.31,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人雖是同一個 卻不見得是聯邦基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠近確定一下不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何靠近？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.42,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從地下去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用衛星殖民地公司的維修用的通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兒是2.27的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約在2百米左右就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會出奇的容易也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.05,0:20:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.79,0:21:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這兒吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還沒到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.09,0:21:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~關著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要開？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到開關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再試試往西的通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.81,0:21:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.11,0:21:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的太空梭只收容在這個區域中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這便是近來禁止閒人進入的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貨櫃一定運來這兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.72,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別嘔氣嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.43,0:21:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的基地就在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說只是知道地點 但也是不簡單呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.03,0:21:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是偶然 但也是大功一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長一定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 你在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.50,0:22:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止這想法 太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.40,0:22:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.80,0:22:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.41,0:22:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不在乎嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.61,0:22:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.11,0:22:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼你才是害怕了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.42,0:22:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了機動戰士就沒膽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.42,0:22:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是那兒 待我到後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.53,0:22:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你便循繩索過去 明白了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.69,0:23:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.59,0:23:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫下太空衣交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是機械運轉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.01,0:23:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.01,0:23:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 停下 會被抓去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.01,0:23:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一項苦差事 好想結束加班快點出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱怨也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.03,0:23:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.80,0:25:27.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}噓をついた夜には
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.51,0:25:33.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠れずに　怖かった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.00,0:25:39.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな喧嘩をしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.30,0:25:47.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}次の日は　忘れていた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.30,0:25:53.80,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空が　青いこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.00,0:26:00.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが　嬉しくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.70,0:26:08.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか人を疑い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.70,0:26:14.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きる寂しさ知る事も
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.90,0:26:20.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつかずに全てを
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.60,0:26:26.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてた頃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.03,0:26:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.03,0:26:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“艾里克斯”怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:00.00,0:27:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克其小姐 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.03,0:27:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁最壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.03,0:27:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 你贏得了那傢夥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.59,0:27:19.90,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,渡過河流 穿越樹林
